{"tid":806951,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"何氏夫婦：口感好似糞便，吐都吐唔切","createTime":"2018-09-05T06:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T05:30:30.000Z","uid":128120,"like":534,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"d231148ae297b6a8812be7285e0cd1caa7029f39","tid":806951,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「口感好似糞便，吐都吐唔切！」何氏夫婦昨午在藍田麗港城商場午膳遇上可怕經歷，在一碟羅漢齋炒麵發現兩塊臭如糞便的異物，何先生一嚐即面色驟變，立時吐出，懷疑遭人「加料」，於是投訴，食環署人員撿走異物化驗，曾拿近一嗅後也說：「真係幾臭！」<br />\n何表示，昨午1時許在一間名叫「香港18」的餐廳午膳，妻子進食羅漢齋炒麵，發現兩大塊糞便狀又臭又怪的異物，何先生初時以為是未泡淋的雲耳，更夾起一試，「一嘢擺落口，粉狀散晒出嚟&hellip;&hellip;口感好似糞便，吐都吐唔切！」<br />\n他們不滿侍應聲稱異物是雲耳，於是報警，同時取走有關炒麵作證據。至下午3時許，兩名食環署人員到何家取走化驗。曾品嚐異物的何先生更是渾身不舒服，狂灌三公升水漱口，仍感到口腔內還殘留那種惡心的臭。《蘋果》曾向餐廳查問，負責人拒絕回應。<br />\n■記者劉永明<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160607/19644259\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160607%2F19644259&d=7sVGgC4E8Ca83h9yExYzNP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0ef99107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160607%2F19644259&h=d27dbb1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160607/19644259</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5ce6fe75dcb9f85be5238f8f91cf5f20101d3a","tid":806951,"uid":10101,"like":660,"dislike":2,"score":658,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"好玩唔玩，玩屎"},{"pid":"8034f24a61f043e5ab628246c89c05c0feb0ebea","tid":806951,"uid":161115,"like":511,"dislike":6,"score":505,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:48:44.000Z","msg":"佢地食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb0bdbd5f4a081fd67b168576958