m/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160607%2F19644259&d=7sVGgC4E8Ca83h9yExYzNP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0ef99107\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160607%2F19644259&h=d27dbb1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160607/19644259</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:12:11.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a681b3fcdefd896a6f8c503eeb07c79476074f69","tid":806951,"uid":91317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"香港18咪即係椰撚閣"},{"pid":"70300eed3eef728559b604902953357f2edd566c","tid":806951,"uid":2949,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"人地就醒 即刻報食環唔使講咁多<br />\n連登果班見到咩異物擺上黎開po屌 叫佢報食環就話碟野俾經理收走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9"},{"pid":"77cebefa99b89b0b657804f7a09ca77241ca1a0a","tid":806951,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"一嘢擺落口，粉狀散晒出嚟&hellip;&hellip;口感好似糞便，吐都吐唔切<br />\n諗起個話面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/